[1]Mwathani Jesũ oragithirio,Nĩ endi mbia Itonga na aremi,Nĩguo watho ndũkagarũrwo.Ngai mũigua tha na Mũtugi,Igua gũkaya na kũriraThĩ-ĩno no ta Misiri.[2]Isaia hinga ici nĩ oigireAtĩ mũnyenda na mĩromo,Na ngoro irĩ kũraya na niĩ[3]Arĩa othe twagocaga nao,Megarurire ta Judasi,Matuĩke thũ na ahĩtithania[4]Murata wakwa ndukamake,Andu a Shaitani makarĩra.Bendera irorete mwaki-inĩ[5]Arĩa mehũraga githũriMena indo ciao cia waganuMahĩtithagie andũ a Mwathani.[6]Thiomi cia thĩ-ĩno nĩ igathira,Tũkaheo thiomi ingĩ igũrũ,Mũndũ onanagie wĩra wake[7]Petero nĩ erire thigari,Mũtikanyambe ta Mwathani,Mũnyambe nyinamite mũtwe
